# CYRUS engineering (Cursor / multi-agent)

## Stack

- **Single dev process:** `npm run dev` from repo root ‚Äî one public port via **`CYRUS_LIVE_PORT`** (`PORT` synced at boot; default 3020); Vite middleware serves `cyrus-ui` on the same origin.
- **API surface:** Use `systemFetch` / `systemApiUrl` from `cyrus-ui/src/lib/system-api.ts` for new browser‚Üíserver calls. Do not add parallel ‚Äúbase URL‚Äù helpers.
- **Lazy Command Center:** `client/` pages rely on same-origin `/api/*` or the fused `fetch` patch when `VITE_CYRUS_API_BASE` is set.

## Auth

- **`REPL_ID` set:** `server/replit_integrations/auth`.
- **Otherwise:** `standalone/auth-adapter.ts` (session + `/api/login` + `/api/auth/user`).

## Wording

- Describe optional **split-origin** or **secondary API** hosts; avoid framing features as ‚ÄúReplit AI‚Äù or ‚ÄúCopilot‚Äù unless the file is Replit-specific runtime (`REPL_ID`).
- Keep comments concise; put long onboarding in **AGENTS.md** or **README**, not scattered in code.

## Safety

- Respect `systemReady` / `GET /api/ready` 503 with `SYSTEM_INITIALIZING` for client retries.
- Run **`npm run typecheck:all`** after non-trivial TypeScript changes.
